## 🌌 The Mission

Planet Earth is experiencing rapid, unprecedented ecological shifts. Forests that were once thriving ecosystems are facing sudden deforestation, canopy thinning, and severe climate stress. 

**ZeryRoot-AI** acts as a decentralized digital shield. By establishing a direct pipeline to international space agencies, the network continuously streams high-resolution satellite imagery and real-time orbital video feeds. The underlying AI automatically cross-references historical environmental baselines with incoming live data streams to isolate anomalies, diagnose climatic/weather root causes, and immediately dispatch actionable intelligence to verified government officials and field guards.

